      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the beverage}}
{{Infobox beverage
| name         = Cola
| image        = [[File:CocaColaBottle background free.jpg|220px|A characteristically shaped [[Coca-Cola]] bottle.]]
| type         = 
| abv          = 
