      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox instrument
|name=Clavichord
|names=[[Italian language|it:]] Clavicordo
|image=Hillclavichord.jpg
|image_capt=1977 clavichord by Keith Hill, op. 44 (opus 28 reworked)
|background=keyboard
|hornbostel_sachs=314.122-4-8
|hornbostel_sachs_desc=Simple [[chordophone]] with [[Musical keyboard|keyboard]] sounded by tangents
|developed=Early 14th century
