! Model of computation

! Resource constraint
|-
| [[DTIME]](''f''(''n''))
| Deterministic Turing machine
| Time ''f''(''n'')
|-
| [[P (complexity)|P]]
| Deterministic Turing machine
| Time poly(''n'')
|-
| [[EXPTIME]]
| Deterministic Turing machine
| Time 2&lt;sup&gt;poly(''n'')&lt;/sup&gt;
|-
| [[NTIME]](''f''(''n''))
| Non-deterministic Turing machine
| Time ''f''(''n'')
|-
| [[NP (complexity)|NP]]
| Non-deterministic Turing machine
| Time poly(''n'')
|-
| [[NEXPTIME]]
| Non-deterministic Turing machine
| Time 2&lt;sup&gt;poly(''n'')&lt;/sup&gt;
|-
| [[DSPACE]](''f''(''n''))
| Deterministic Turing machine
| Space ''f''(''n'')
|-
